Comment: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}看着你的侧脸
Comment: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}所注视着的
Comment: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:29.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}是下个季节
Comment: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:33.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}我明白的
Comment: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:37.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}痛彻心扉
Comment: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:42.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}却反射似的故做笑容
Comment: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:49.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}暧昧的线条在摇动的缝隙中
Comment: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:55.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}用天真的小聪明  连结着梦境
Comment: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:56.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}
Comment: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.94,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}满是谎言 （别离开我）
Comment: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:01.99,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}遍体磷伤  （能不能留下）
Comment: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:06.76,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}只有纯度高过一切
Comment: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:11.00,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}看啊  多么地耀眼（我该说些什么）
Comment: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.14,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}泪水结成的钻石
Comment: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:18.86,EDCN-b,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}一切的终结就要开始
Comment: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:25.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)\blur10.5}这永远无法忘记的季节
